    "description": "The StorageTek™ T10000C Tape Drive provides 5 TB native capacity and 240 MB/sec throughput using BaFe media and with backward read compatibility to the T10000A/B. Designed for maximum security and performance, the T10000C provides AES-256 encryption to protect and authenticate customer data and to provide secure, authenticated transmission of key material. Designed for maximum performance, the drive allows the use of multiple keys per tape with a cache memory to minimize the overhead of key transmission. Works seamlessly with the Oracle OKM to provide a secure end-to-end management solution.",
